poispkgs

An R package to install and attach CRAN and GitHub Packages commonly used in Poisson Consulting analyses in the preferred order.

Demonstration

search()

Installation

To install the latest development version from GitHub

# install.packages("remotes")
remotes::install_github("poissonconsulting/poispkgs")

Or to install from the Poisson drat repository

# install.packages("drat")
drat::addRepo("poissonconsulting")
install.packages("poispkgs")
